Quest:All Access Pass

From Wizard101 Wiki
Jump to: navigation, search

Quest Information


Prequest:
My Pen!

Given By: Hathi Irontrunk

Giver Location: Stone Town
This is a storyline quest.

Goals:
Talk to Rakstede Steelhorn
Talk to Lail Brighteyes (in Darajani Zoo)
Hand In: Lail Brighteyes

Reward:

80
2,690


Leads to:

Class Is Very Entertaining

Quest Dialogue


This page is for recording a complete Quest Dialogue of all the conversation and story during a quest.
This includes NPC discussions, Narrator statements, and Creature speeches.


Documentation on how to edit this page can be found at Template:QuestInfobox/doc.

Hints, guides, and discussions of the Wiki content related to All Access Pass should be placed in the Wiki Page Discussion Forums.

Search for content related to All Access Pass in the Central Wiki Forums by clicking here.
